high_descs: Walk forward through the doorway on the opposite side of the room and walk to the left corner of the table.
Pick up the lid from the table.
Walk around to the opposite side of the table.
Put the lid in the cardboard box.
Pick up the cardboard box from the table.
Walk around to the opposite side of the table, then walk through the doorway until you reach the glass table.
Put the cardboard box down on the glass table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cardboard box with a lid inside of it on the glass table.

high_descs: Move across the room and walk through the doorway into the next room with a table.
Pick the round object up from the left corner of the table.
Carry the round object around the table until you're standing on the opposite side of the table, so you're facing the doorway.
Place the round object in the open box on the table.
Pick up the box with the round object from the table.
Carry the box around the table and through the doorway until you get to the coffee table.
Place the box with the round object on it on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Move a boxed item from one room to a coffee table in a different room.

high_descs: Walk across the room, go through the door, walk to the dining room table.
Pick up the bowl on the table.
Walk around the table, face the box on the table.
Place the bowl in the box on the table.
Pick up the box off of the table.
Walk back through the door, walk to the coffee table.
Place the box on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put the bowl in the box on the coffee table.
